title: How Ryan Trahan Gained 4 Million Subscribers in 1 Year
description: Ryan Trahan has gone from making videos about beating his mile time to being one of the fastest growing creators on the platform. In this episode of Creator Economics, he breaks down his creator journey, vision for his channel, and how he's found success on the platform.
dc:creator: Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins
